A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Article 6 of Chapter 13 of Title 16 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
2 relating to kratom, so as to provide for registration of kratom products and sworn
3 certification of compliance; to provide for applicability; to provide for publication of
4 registration information; to revise penalties; to provide for definitions; to provide for related
5 matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 Article 6 of Chapter 13 of Title 16 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
9 kratom, is amended in Code Section 16-13-120, relating to definitions, by adding new
10 paragraphs to read as follows:
11 "(1.1) 'Approved kratom delivery form' means a kratom product registered in accordance
12 with Code Section 16-13-123.
13 (1.2) 'Department' means the Department of Agriculture."
14 SECTION 2.
15 Said article is further amended by adding a new Code section to read as follows:
